- Position: bottom-right corner, 120x120px collapsed, 280px expanded
- Background: glass-morphism card with gradient border (purple→pink→rose)

KIRA BEHAVIOR:

On Application Launch (after login):
1. Kira slides up from bottom-right with Framer Motion spring animation
2. Detects time of day via JS Date:
