4. Kira says: "I'm Kira, your STHENIA assistant! I'm here to help you with flexible 
   work requests, wellbeing tracking, counselling, meal planning, reminders, 
   and so much more. What can I do for you today? 💜"
5. Kira's mouth Lottie state transitions: idle → talking → idle
6. Kira does a small wave animation during greeting

